---
description: Vitest testing patterns for agentic-setup
globs: tests/**
---

- Vitest config: `vitest.config.ts` · Setup: `tests/setup.ts`
- Run all: `npm run test` · Single: `npx vitest run tests/scoring/accuracy.test.ts`
- Coverage: `npm run test:coverage` (v8 provider)
- LLM calls globally mocked in `tests/setup.ts` — never call real providers
- Use `vi.mock()` for `fs`, `child_process` · `vi.mocked()` for type-safe assertions
- Tests mirror `src/`: `tests/llm/config.test.ts` tests `src/llm/config.ts`
- Pattern: `describe` → `beforeEach(vi.clearAllMocks)` → `it` with `expect`
- Environment vars: save in `beforeEach`, restore in `afterEach`
